trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of non-selectable dates in a <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling med ikke-valgbar datoer i en <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection contains <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarDateRange> objects that specify multiple dates that cannot be selected by a user.
trans-unit.target: CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection inneholder <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarDateRange>objekter som angir flere datoer som kan velges av en bruker.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarDateRange>

trans-unit.source: To make all past dates not selectable, you can use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection.AddDatesInPast%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil at alle forbi datoer ikke kan velges, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection.AddDatesInPast%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.CalendarBlackoutDatesCollection.AddDatesInPast%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"></xref> whose dates this object represents.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Calendar"> </xref> med datoer som representerer for dette objektet.

trans-unit.source: Adds all dates before <xref:System.DateTime.Today*> to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til alle datoer før <xref:System.DateTime.Today*>i samlingen.</xref:System.DateTime.Today*>

trans-unit.source: Use this method to prevent users from selecting dates that are in the past.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden for å forhindre brukere fra å velge datoer som er i fortiden.
